{
  "page": "Ethan Glover",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Glover\" title=\"House Glover\"><img alt=\"House Glover.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/41/House_Glover.svg/50px-House_Glover.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/41/House_Glover.svg/75px-House_Glover.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/41/House_Glover.svg/100px-House_Glover.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Ethan Glover</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Glover\" title=\"House Glover\"><img alt=\"House Glover.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/41/House_Glover.svg/50px-House_Glover.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/41/House_Glover.svg/75px-House_Glover.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/41/House_Glover.svg/100px-House_Glover.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Ethan_Glover_TheMico.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Ethan Glover TheMico.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d0/Ethan_Glover_TheMico.jpg/350px-Ethan_Glover_TheMico.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"495\" srcset=\"/images/d/d0/Ethan_Glover_TheMico.jpg 1.5x\" /></a><div>Ethan Glover, by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://themicos.blogspot.com/\">The Mico</a> ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Glover\" title=\"House Glover\">House Glover</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">Northmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\nor before <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_274_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">274&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/283_AC\" title=\"283 AC\">283&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><br />the <a href=\"/index.php/Combat_at_the_tower_of_joy\" title=\"Combat at the tower of joy\">tower of joy</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Buried</th><td>\nthe tower of joy, Dorne</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Ethan Glover</b> was a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Glover\" title=\"House Glover\">House Glover</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a>. He was the <a href=\"/index.php/Squire\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Squire\">squire</a> for <a href=\"/index.php/Brandon_Stark\" title=\"Brandon Stark\">Brandon Stark</a>, the heir of <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ethan_Glover&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>When <a href=\"/index.php/Brandon_Stark\" title=\"Brandon Stark\">Brandon Stark</a> learned of his sister <a href=\"/index.php/Lyanna_Stark\" title=\"Lyanna Stark\">Lyanna's</a> abduction at the hands of <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaegar Targaryen\">Rhaegar Targaryen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Prince_of_Dragonstone\" title=\"Prince of Dragonstone\">Prince of Dragonstone</a>, he took off for <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> with <a href=\"/index.php/Jeffory_Mallister\" title=\"Jeffory Mallister\">Jeffory Mallister</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Kyle_Royce\" title=\"Kyle Royce\">Kyle Royce</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Elbert_Arryn\" title=\"Elbert Arryn\">Elbert Arryn</a>, and his squire, Ethan. When Brandon entered the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a> and demanded that Rhaegar come out and die, King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a> had Brandon's party arrested for threatening the life of the crown prince. The fathers of Brandon and his companions were called to King's Landing to answer for the crimes of their sons. The king had the fathers and sons all executed, with only Ethan spared.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Aerys then demanded that <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Arryn\" title=\"Jon Arryn\">Jon Arryn</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Eyrie\" title=\"Lord of the Eyrie\">Lord of the Eyrie</a>, execute his <a href=\"/index.php/Ward\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ward\">wards</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert Baratheon</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Lord of Storm&#39;s End\">Lord of Storm's End</a>, and Brandon's younger brother <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a>, now <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Lord of Winterfell\">Lord of Winterfell</a>. However, Jon refused the king's command, and <a href=\"/index.php/Robert%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Robert&#39;s Rebellion\">Robert's Rebellion</a> started shortly thereafter.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>After Aerys's death in the <a href=\"/index.php/Sack_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"Sack of King&#39;s Landing\">Sack of King's Landing</a>, Eddard lifted the <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Siege of Storm&#39;s End\">siege of Storm's End</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Lord Stark then rode to the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Mountains\" title=\"Red Mountains\">Red Mountains</a> with Ethan, <a href=\"/index.php/Martyn_Cassel\" title=\"Martyn Cassel\">Martyn Cassel</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Theo_Wull\" title=\"Theo Wull\">Theo Wull</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Howland_Reed\" title=\"Howland Reed\">Howland Reed</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Mark_Ryswell\" title=\"Mark Ryswell\">Mark Ryswell</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Willam_Dustin\" title=\"Willam Dustin\">Willam Dustin</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Barrowton\" title=\"Lord of Barrowton\">Lord of Barrowton</a>. At the <a href=\"/index.php/Tower_of_joy\" title=\"Tower of joy\">tower of joy</a>, they were confronted by the last three members of Aerys's <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Arthur_Dayne\" title=\"Arthur Dayne\">Arthur Dayne</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Oswell_Whent\" title=\"Oswell Whent\">Oswell Whent</a>, and Lord Commander <a href=\"/index.php/Gerold_Hightower\" title=\"Gerold Hightower\">Gerold Hightower</a>. All but Eddard and Howland were slain in the ensuing <a href=\"/index.php/Combat_at_the_tower_of_joy\" title=\"Combat at the tower of joy\">fight</a>. Afterwards, Eddard had the tower pulled down, and used its stones for cairns for the fallen.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ethan_Glover&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ethan_Glover&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>During a fever dream, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a> recalls Ethan and his other former companions at the tower of joy.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ethan_Glover&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a> tells Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a> that of <a href=\"/index.php/Brandon_Stark\" title=\"Brandon Stark\">Brandon Stark</a>'s companions who were arrested by King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a>, Ethan was the only one to survive.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ethan_Glover&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>In the dream his friends rode with him, as they had in life. Proud <a href=\"/index.php/Martyn_Cassel\" title=\"Martyn Cassel\">Martyn Cassel</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Jory_Cassel\" title=\"Jory Cassel\">Jory</a>'s father; faithful <a href=\"/index.php/Theo_Wull\" title=\"Theo Wull\">Theo Wull</a>; Ethan Glover, who had been <a href=\"/index.php/Brandon_Stark\" title=\"Brandon Stark\">Brandon</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Squire\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Squire\">squire</a>; Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Mark_Ryswell\" title=\"Mark Ryswell\">Mark Ryswell</a>, soft of speech and gentle of heart; the <a href=\"/index.php/Crannogman\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Crannogman\">crannogman</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Howland_Reed\" title=\"Howland Reed\">Howland Reed</a>; Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Willam_Dustin\" title=\"Willam Dustin\">Dustin</a> on his great red <a href=\"/index.php/Horse\" title=\"Horse\">stallion</a>. Ned had known their faces as well as he knew his own once, but the years leech at a man's memories, even those he has vowed never to forget. In the dream they were only shadows, grey wraiths on horses made of mist.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Jaime</b>: <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys</a> sent <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen_guards\" title=\"House Targaryen guards\">his guards</a> to arrest them all for plotting <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaegar Targaryen\">his son's</a> murder. The others were <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lords</a>' sons too, it seems to me.<br />\n<b>Catelyn</b>: Ethan Glover was <a href=\"/index.php/Brandon_Stark\" title=\"Brandon Stark\">Brandon's</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Squire\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Squire\">squire</a>. He was the only one to survive.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ethan_Glover&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Ethan's